==English==

===Pronunciation===
{{rfp}}

====Hyphenation====
'''pup·pet'''

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# Any small model of a person or animal able to be moved by strings or in the form of a [[glove]].
# A [[doll]].
# (''figuratively'') A person, country, etc, controlled by another.

